               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Thermazene<sup>®</sup> is a soft, white, water dispersible cream containing the antimicrobial agent silver sulfadiazine in micronized form for topical application.  Each gram of silver sulfadiazine cream contains 10mg of micronized silver sulfadiazine.<br/>       This active agent has the following structural formula:</paragraph>
                  <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="mm01"/>
                  <paragraph>Silver sulfadiazine cream contains 1% w/w silver sulfadiazine.  The vehicle in which the active ingredient is dispersed consists of water, stearyl alcohol, white petrolatum, polyoxyl 40 stearate, propylene glycol, isopropyl myristate, and sorbitan monooleate with 0.3% methylparaben as a preservative.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20140116"/>
               <component>
                  <observationMedia classCode="OBS" moodCode="EVN" ID="mm01">
                     <text>Structural Formula</text>
                     <value xsi:type="ED" mediaType="image/jpeg">
                        <reference value="structural formula.jpg"/>
                     </value>
                  </observationMedia>
               </component>
            </section>
         </component>
