               <title>REFERENCES</title>
               <text>
                  <list listType="ordered" ID="f5436aa0-d008-4bd6-b687-d826106da4cb">
                     <item>Caffee F, Bingham H. Leukopenia and silver sulfadiazine. J Trauma. 1982;22: 586–587.</item>
